Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
hallo
Hi how can I help
Hello, how can I help?
I am interested in viewing an apartment.
You suddenly remember that you have a hot date on Wednesday at 10 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
What is your name
Could you give me your name, please?
I'm John! I was going to ask for a a time on Wednesday at 10pm, but now I remember I have a hot date then!
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
What location
What apartment are you interested in?
I'd like Shadyside Apartments. Do they have a pool? It would be a great place to bring my hot date!

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
Yes there is a pool. Do you know if you paid a application fee?
Yes there is a pool. Do you know if you paid a application fee?
No idea if I paid it. What times do you have available?
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your hot date. [instruction 5 of 6]
Yes 2 pm on Tuesday is available.
Yes 2 pm on Tuesday is available.
Okay I'll take that. Now I have to decide where to take my hot date. Maybe I'll find a good movie.
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
